{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}
<!-- Please place categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata (see [[Wikipedia:Wikidata]]) -->

== Usage ==

As supported by [[Wikipedia:Wikimedia sister projects]], this template may be used to add a [[Wikivoyage]] link to a Wikipedia article. It generates an [[Help:Interwikimedia links|interwikimedia link]] – it is not intended to represent [[WP:SOURCES|sources]] for Wikipedia articles. It should only be used as an "External link", never as a citation.

The template can be used with one, two or no parameters as follows:
:'''<nowiki>{{Wikivoyage inline}}</nowiki>''' creates a link to the Wikivoyage page matching the Wikipedia page name.
:'''<nowiki>{{Wikivoyage inline|Boracay}}</nowiki>''' creates a link to the Wikivoyage page titled "Boracay".
:'''<nowiki>{{Wikivoyage inline|Boracay|Boracay Island}}</nowiki>''' creates a link to the Wikivoyage page titled "Boracay", but the link is worded "Boracay Island".

== See also ==
* [[Template:Wikivoyage]]
* [[Template:Wikivoyage listing]]
* [[Template:Wikisource redirect]]
{{Commons templates see also}}

==TemplateData==
{{TemplateData header}}
<templatedata>
{
	"params": {
		"1": {
			"label": "Page name of Wikivoyage Article",
			"description": "Specify the exact name of the Wikivoyage article, as specified in the URL after \"wiki/\"  This field is used to look up the Wikivoyage article.",
			"example": "London (Ontario)",
			"type": "string"
		},
		"2": {
			"label": "User friendly name of Wikivoyage article",
			"description": "This is the text that will be displayed to identify the name of the place or topic of the Wikivoyage article",
			"example": "\"London\" or \"London, Ontario\" or \"London, ON\"",
			"type": "string"
		},
		"list": {},
		"links": {},
		"extratext": {}
	},
	"description": "This template is intended for adding an external link within a Wikipedia article to the corresponding Wikivoyage article.  If the Wikipedia and Wikivoyage articles are identical, no parameters need to be set.",
	"paramOrder": [
		"1",
		"2",
		"list",
		"links",
		"extratext"
	]
}
</templatedata>
<includeonly>{{sandbox other||
<!-- Categories below this line, please; interwikis at Wikidata -->
[[Category:Inline interwiki link templates]]
[[Category:Wikivoyage templates|Inline]]
}}</includeonly>

